reviews.text: Not much going on here.  Everything was hot.  Mozzarella Sticks were out of the bag, however they were the quality ones.  Marinara was cold & would make a better gazpacho, not much flavor.  Cheeseburger was hot & toasted.  Mayo & veggies were ok, not a fan of the provolone which has no flavor.  No seasoning either, burger had zero flavor‚Ä¶

I been order Medium heat wings from wild wings forever‚Ä¶.never never had this saucy mess of a hot sauce on them and not to mention they arrived COLD! Very disappointing,do better wild wings!
They did give us a $20 credit since my wife‚Äôs wings arrived cold as well! üöÆüöÆüöÆ

Excellent wings! This is the place we always order from for wings. Quick delivery (helps to tip your driver wellüòâ).

We like our wings crispy, there's an option for that and they do a great job.

Old and butter is my bread and butter. üòÅüòã

Wings were oily and the sauce was soupy. Most were drained into the plastic bag before I got home.Bought mild wings and garlic parm. It tasted like the wings were past their 'best before date' when fried. Wings were chewy.The fries were extra greasy too. Atmosphere is basic wings joint..nowhere to dine in. One worker there .She was nice enough. Overall won't return. Wings are awful.

Called at 6pm, they charged my card shortly after stating delivery would be 30 to 45 minutes, an hour and 15 minutes later we called asking where our food was and as we were left on speaker phone the cashier was explaining it to someone who basically stated that there was no order, and that if we had paid there would be an order, basically calling us liers... till the order was found on the screen. Then no apology or explanation that the food would be late just that it was on the way. Poor customer service. Food arrived an hour and 22 minutes after being ordered

recentReviews.text: Called at 6pm, they charged my card shortly after stating delivery would be 30 to 45 minutes, an hour and 15 minutes later we called asking where our food was and as we were left on speaker phone the cashier was explaining it to someone who basically stated that there was no order, and that if we had paid there would be an order, basically calling us liers... till the order was found on the screen. Then no apology or explanation that the food would be late just that it was on the way. Poor customer service. Food arrived an hour and 22 minutes after being ordered

recentReviews.author: Ray Metzger II
recentReviews.text: Not much going on here.  Everything was hot.  Mozzarella Sticks were out of the bag, however they were the quality ones.  Marinara was cold & would make a better gazpacho, not much flavor.  Cheeseburger was hot & toasted.  Mayo & veggies were ok, not a fan of the provolone which has no flavor.  No seasoning either, burger had zero flavor‚Ä¶

recentReviews.author: natasha hillocks
recentReviews.text: Wings were oily and the sauce was soupy. Most were drained into the plastic bag before I got home.Bought mild wings and garlic parm. It tasted like the wings were past their 'best before date' when fried. Wings were chewy.The fries were extra greasy too. Atmosphere is basic wings joint..nowhere to dine in. One worker there .She was nice enough. Overall won't return. Wings are awful.
